 src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-NK3SZPP\"\n    height=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"display:none;visibility:hidden\"></iframe></noscript>\n\n\n\n  \n  <div class='new-ui-modal-full-page-wrapper' id='photo_viewer'>\n<div class='new-ui-modal-overlay'>\n<div class='viewer-header'>\n<div class='close-button'>\n<div class='button-icon-small'>\n<div class='button-touch-area'>\n<div class='icon-button'>\n<i class='wt-icon wt-icon-close'></i>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class='pager'>\n<div class='page'>1</div>\n<div class='slash'>/</div>\n<div class='total'>5</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id='photo_viewer_content_wrapper'>\n<div id='photo_viewer_content'></div>\n<div class='side-button left-button'>\n<div class='button-icon-small'>\n<div class='button-touch-area'>\n<div class='icon-button'>\n<div class='icon-button-cover'></div>\n<i class='wt-icon wt-icon-chevron-left'></i>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class='side-button right-button'>\n<div class='button-icon-small'>\n<div class='button-touch-area'>\n<div class='icon-button'>\n<div class='icon-button-cover'></div>\n<i class='wt-icon wt-icon-chevron-right'></i>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n  <div id=\"fb-root\"></div>\n  <div id=\"container\">\n    <div id=\"main-outer\" class=\"cf\">\n        \n      \n\n      <div id=\"main\" class=\"company-registrations-controller company-registrations-trial action-trial cf\">\n        <div id=\"main-inner\" class=\"cf\">\n          <div class='wrapper'>\n<div class='left'>\n<div class='header'>\n<div class='logo'>\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"/about/list?utm_campaign=trial_registered\"><img src=\"https://wantedly-assets.wantedly.com/static/logo/logo-color-BrandColorBG.svg\" />\n</a></div>\n<div class='text'>採用担当者様へ</div>\n</div>\n<div class='top'>\n<div class='top-image'>\n<img src=\"https://dubpy8abnqmkw.cloudfront.net/images/company-registration-trial/jpn/eyecatch_pc.png\" />\n</div>\n<div class='top-inner'>\n<div class='catchphrase'>さぁ、新しい採用の世界へ。</div>\n<div class='title'>まずは､30日の<br>無料トライアルで。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class='content'>\n<section class='company-page'>\n<div class='title'>\n<div class='background-image'>\n<img src=\"https://dubpy8abnqmkw.cloudfront.net/images/company-registration-trial/jpn/01.svg\" />\n</div>\n<div class='text'>採用に特化した会社ページが作れる</div>\n</div>\n<div class='image'>\n<img src=\"https://dubpy8abnqmkw.cloudfront.net/images/company-registration-trial/jpn/section_image_01.png\" />\n</div>\n<div class='description'>簡単なフォーマット入力で、自社の魅力を詰め込んだ会社ページが作成できます。検索エンジンやSNS経由での流入に強く、採用ホームページとしてもお使いいただけます。</div>\n</section>\n<section class='projects'>\n<div class='title'>\n<div class='background-image'>\n<img src=\"https://dubpy8abnqmkw.cloudfront.net/images/company-registration-trial/jpn/02.svg\" />\n</div>\n<div class='text'>共感を生む募集が公開できる</div>\n</div>\n<div class='image'>\n<img src=\"https://dubpy8abnqmkw.cloudfront.net/images/company-registration-trial/jpn/section_image_02.png\" />\n</div>\n<div class='description'>有料プランと同様の管理画面から、最大で5つの募集を作成できます。エントリーした最初の5人までは、無料トライアル期間でメッセージのやり取りも可能です。</div>\n</section>\n<section class='stories'>\n<div class='title'>\n<div class='background-image'>\n<img src=\"https://dubpy8abnqmkw.cloudfront.net/images/company-registration-trial/jpn/03.svg\" />\n</div>\n<div class='text'>記事で会社の魅力を拡散できる</div>\n</div>\n<div class='image'>\n<img src=\"https://dubpy8abnqmkw.cloudfront.net/images/company-registration-trial/jpn/section_image_03.png\" />\n</div>\n<div class='description'>募集では伝えきれない自社の魅力を発信できる、ブログ機能が利用できます。社員インタビューで共感度を高めたり、オフィス紹介によって候補者のイメージを膨らませたりすることで、ブランディングや採用広報としてご利用いただけます。</div>\n</section>\n<div class='pricing'>\n<div class='title'>基本機能はどれだけ使っても、<br>毎月定額、成果報酬なし</div>\n<div class='description'>基本機能はどれだけ使っても毎月定額、成果報酬なし。Wantedlyは、運用の工夫で採用単価が抑えられ、使えば使うほどお客様に採用効果を感じていただけるよう、毎月定額の料金モデルを採用しています。</div>\n<div class='button'>\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"/external_links/price_serviceguide_download?ad_params%5Butm_campaign%5D=trial_registered\">料金表を見る</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class='footer'>\n<div class='links'>\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://wantedly.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/204214429\">推奨環境</a>\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://help.wantedly.com/hc/ja\">ヘルプ</a>\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://service-terms.wantedly.com/user_terms/ja_JP\">利用規約</a>\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://service-terms.wantedly.com/privacy_policy/ja_JP\">プライバシーポリシー</a>\n</div>\n<div class='line'></div>\n<div class='company'>\n<div class='logo'>\n<a href=\"/about/list?utm_campaign=trial_registered\"><img src=\"https://wantedly-assets.wantedly.com/static/logo/logo-color-LightBG.svg\" />\n</a></div>\n<div class='text'>@2022 Wantedly, Inc.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class='right'>\n<div class='content'>\n<div class='title'>登録は簡単、<br>フォーム入力のみ。</div>\n<div class='description'>フォーム入力後すぐに無料トライアルをご利用いただけます</div>\n<div class='form trial-form'>\n<form class=\"new_client_inquiry trial_form\" id=\"new_client_inquiry\" data-sitekey=\"6LfsR8QZAAAAANG-zNJDjb_3ZiPaqy3ZkSPzbamq\" action=\"/company_registrations/done_trial?require_url=unrequired\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"APm6fefvqxL43DJhYagUS+SpLldF0P93LRNz9PBYDY7ImxjL5xnY57LB3TjuhevrW2mwaUcbPr1C+y9OrWtG/A==\" autocomplete=\"off\" /><input value=\"trial\" autocomplete=\"off\" type=\"hidden\" name=\"client_inquiry[plan]\" id=\"client_inquiry_plan\" />\n<label for=\"client_inquiry_company_name\">会社名</label>\n<div class='input-field'>\n<input placeholder=\"会社名\" autofocus=\"autofocus\" class=\"need-check allow_submit\" required=\"required\" autocomplete=\"off\" type=\"text\" name=\"client_inquiry[company_name]\" id=\"client_inquiry_company_name\" />\n</div>\n<div class='error-message-blank' id='error_blank_for_client_inquiry_company_name'>　</div>\n<div class='error-message-require' id='error_require_for_client_inquiry_company_name'>会社名は必須項目です</div>\n<label for=\"client_inquiry_use